result.name: Ching Chong CockN'Ball Dungeon

reviews.text: Tables fool of decent food and cold beer, fantastic way to start a night on a budget. This place is an institution. Don't expect fancy service and bespoke cocktails, come for the experience and you won't be dissapointed. * Not for picky eaters, food arrives on the table for you to pick and choose from. If you're cool with that this should be perfect. But is worth considering if you have any specific dietary requirements.

So accommodating, friendly and cheerful! Went in alone and 3 beers turned up in front of me straight away. The boss came over and had a good old chat. Top notch grub. Would come back tomorrow if I wasn't leaving!

Great restaurant for students! We were a group of 6 students from Austria, for only 80 HKD/p.p we got as much food as we wanted and more than enough drinks. The lady serving us was really friendly and especially the Thai chicken was more than awesome!
It was great. Amazing. I loved it. I will keep it near and dear to my heart. The dungeon is the best place to be. The men are amazing and the food is delectable. A true 5 star rating.
This is an HK institution. Distinctly average food but actually fine. Beer is cold and free flow. $80 unlimited. Mr Wong is a legend too. Staff are friendly. Recommended.
